title: Independent Candidate Shahabuddin Khan wins PP-280 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 10 (APP): Independent Candidate, Shahabuddin Khan has won the Punjab Assembly election from PP-280, Layyah-II by securing 39,057 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Malik Abdul Shakoor Sawag of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) who bagged 26,942 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 58.94%.
